Thank you for subscribing to <%= @plan.name %>!

<%- if @plan.has_feature?(:mentor) -%>
You will receive an email from your mentor soon.
<%- end -%>

Feel free to respond to this email and give us an idea of your background,
experience, and what you'd like to learn next. We'll respond with some
pointers for where to get started.

<%- if @plan.has_feature?(:exercises) %>
In additon, one of the first things you might do is visit our Trail Maps
and check off your skills to identify new things to learn:
<%= trails_url %>
<%- end -%>

<%= @plan.name %> also includes access to our forum. Get help
from thoughtbot and other subscribers here:
<%= Forum.url %>

If you have any customer support or billing questions, please email us at
<%= ENV["SUPPORT_EMAIL"] %>.
